#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:1
msgid "2018-Specific Changes"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:3
msgid ""
"The following is a summary of changes that only apply to code compiled with "
"the 2018 edition compared to the 2015 edition."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:6
msgid "[Path changes](module-system/path-clarity.md):"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:7
msgid "Paths in `use` declarations work the same as other paths."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:8
msgid "Paths starting with `::` must be followed with an external crate."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:9
msgid ""
"Paths in `pub(in path)` visibility modifiers must start with `crate`, "
"`self`, or `super`."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:11
msgid ""
"[Anonymous trait function parameters](trait-system/no-anon-params.md) are "
"not allowed."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:12
msgid ""
"[Trait function parameters](https://doc.rust-lang.org/stable/reference/items/"
"traits.html#parameter-patterns) may use any irrefutable pattern when the "
"function has a body."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:14
msgid ""
"[`dyn`](trait-system/dyn-trait-for-trait-objects.md) is a [strict keyword]"
"(https://doc.rust-lang.org/reference/keywords.html#strict-keywords), in 2015 "
"it is a [weak keyword](https://doc.rust-lang.org/reference/keywords."
"html#weak-keywords)."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:15
msgid ""
"`async`, `await`, and `try` are [reserved keywords](https://doc.rust-lang."
"org/reference/keywords.html#reserved-keywords)."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:16
msgid "The following lints are now deny by default:"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:17
msgid ""
"[tyvar_behind_raw_pointer](https://github.com/rust-lang/rust/issues/46906)"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:19
msgid "Cargo"
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:20
msgid ""
"If there is a target definition in a `Cargo.toml` manifest, it no longer "
"automatically disables automatic discovery of other targets."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:22
msgid ""
"Target paths of the form `src/{target_name}.rs` are no longer inferred for "
"targets where the `path` field is not set."
msgstr ""

#: src/rust-2018/edition-changes.md:24
msgid ""
"`cargo install` for the current directory is no longer allowed, you must "
"specify `cargo install --path .` to install the current package."
msgstr ""
